{"tid":2275942,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句經典愛情電影對白","createTime":"2020-11-07T13:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T11:18:37.000Z","uid":33041,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f986a121f880e070eb054257cc55beebadef7b73","tid":2275942,"uid":33041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"&quot;I love you, Dex, so much.  I just don't like you anymore.  I'm sorry.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n有時覺得一切都過咗去，所有嘢都完結咗<br />\n係應該要好好做人，好好愛自己<br />\n但每次諗起過去嘅傷痛重係覺得好憎自己竟然放任人一再傷害自己，又好憤怒點解一個我咁愛嘅人會咁樣傷害我<br />\n希望2021年真係可以thank you, next<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入嚟放低句電影對白同感受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2186f216bbc0d414ce7bf6ef144e53a92e67bc9","tid":2275942,"uid":369643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"好番未啊你"},{"pid":"8831f86cf8e33050b3e063f6f95988f073dab4e9","tid":2275942,"uid":33041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2186f216bbc0d414ce7bf6ef144e53a92e67bc9","tid":2275942,"uid":369643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"好番未啊你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"7788啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4907897dcef3326b75d1a1fea560eb0b4a7f54e6","tid":2275942,"uid":144312,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"你養我呀？<br />\n<br />\n係呀！<br />\n<br />\n你養掂自己先啦"},{"pid":"6660bcd16bf01f0a06d5065eac90f6836f097583","tid":2275942,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"捷克斯洛伐克"},{"pid":"f10996a5808577395a63831c898158478f193be5","tid":2275942,"uid":316590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:38:39.000Z","msg":"I wrote you 365 letters"},{"pid":"cfb6b3ff47a07b8c892d5a999b384cfec27d9926","tid":2275942,"uid":33041,"like":1,"disli